                  SECT. III. Miſſall Sacrifice againſt reaſon.
                  IN reaſon, there muſt be in euerie Sacrifice (as Cardinall Bellarmine grants) a deſtruction of the thing offered; and ſhall we ſay that they make their Sauiour to crucifie him againe?Bell. l. 1. de Miſſa, cap. 2.
                      No, but to eat him; For (Conſumptio ſeu manducatio quae ſit à

